# To-Do List Application

## Description
This is a simple command-line To-Do List application developed using Python. It allows users to add tasks and view their task list.

## Features
>Add new tasks
>View all tasks
>Simple menu-driven interface

## Technologies Used
>Python 3

## How to Run
>> Open the project in Pydroid 3 or any Python IDE.
>> Run the `todo.py` file.
>> Follow the on-screen menu.

